flowchart LR
    EU["<b>EU AI Act</b><br><span style='font-size:12px;color:#6d28d9'>a binding law</span><br><br><b>Who issues it:</b> The European Union<br><b>Who must obey:</b> Anyone in scope, by law<br><b>How easily undone:</b> Hard — it is a law<br><b>Reach:</b> Broad"]

    NIST["<b>NIST AI RMF</b><br><span style='font-size:12px;color:#6d28d9'>voluntary guidance</span><br><br><b>Who issues it:</b> NIST — a US agency<br><b>Who must obey:</b> No one — chosen freely<br><b>How easily undone:</b> Not applicable — optional<br><b>Reach:</b> As broad as you choose"]

    EO["<b>EO 14110</b><br><span style='font-size:12px;color:#6d28d9'>a US Presidential order</span><br><br><b>Who issues it:</b> The US President<br><b>Who must obey:</b> US federal agencies, plus some industry reporting<br><b>How easily undone:</b> Easy — a later President can revoke it<br><b>Reach:</b> Narrower — mainly directs the government"]

